</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="8.[168,1347,1527,1577]" box="[168,1273,1554,1577]" pageId="8" pageNumber="103">
before urbanization of the area, shows a typical habitat for 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hendel" authorityYear="1914" box="[734,884,1554,1577]" class="Insecta" family="Platystomatidae" genus="Microepicausta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="103" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
